WEBVTT

00:08:01.208 --> 00:08:02.409
Hapana, hawawezi.

00:08:02.433 --> 00:08:05.909
(Kicheko) (Makofi)

00:08:05.933 --> 00:08:07.480
Hivyo sasa unaweza kuuliza

00:08:08.504 --> 00:08:12.136
kwanini uwongo wa watoto
ni vigumu kuugundua.

00:08:12.958 --> 00:08:15.970
Ngoja niwaonyeshe hili
na mtoto wangu mwenyewe, Nathan

00:08:15.994 --> 00:08:18.163
Hii ni hisia za uso wake


00:08:18.187 --> 00:08:19.571
anapodanganya.

00:08:19.595 --> 00:08:21.801
(Kicheko)

00:08:21.825 --> 00:08:23.427
Hivyo wakati watoto wanadanganya,

00:08:23.451 --> 00:08:26.607
hisia za nyuso zao
ni za kawaida.

00:08:27.123 --> 00:08:30.583
Ingawa nyuma ya hii hisia ya kawaida,